reviewText: I absolutely Love this DVD!! An Incredible Worship Experience!!
Israel is one of my favorite artist.

Just another classic by Israel & New Breed. Such a diversity in song style but yet still true to his musical excellence along with his pointed spiritual messages. My strength, Our God reigns pushing back the darkness. In the name of Jesus, Covered & it's already done. Thank u God, thank u Israel.  Love it
Powerful DVD, Israel and New Breed has done it again! They have a global sound that reaches the nations,the worship that takes place on the album is indescribable and extraordinary!

I am a die hard Israel & New Breed fan, so much that I saw the movie when it was in theaters back in January.  If you saw it in the movies, you might be disappointed that none of the commentary and the discussion at the end of the premiere in the movies is on this DVD.  I would have preferred that the DVD had been exactly what I saw in the movies.  Oh well, I love the music and will still enjoy
Love it!  It blesses me every time I watch it.

The music was very nice. What I didn't like on the DVD was that every few seconds the camara view changed. It was hard to enjoy the view for me. His other DVDs were not like this one. His other ones were great. If I would have known this I would have just ordered the cd.
